or and GraphQL. Let’s build a truly engaging next gen application and push Blazor to the limit. <a href=\"https://slides.com/michaelingmarstaib/developer-week-building-modern-applications-with-graphql-and-blazor\">Slides</a>. <a href=\"https://github.com/michaelstaib/PublicSpeaking/tree/master/jetbrains_net_days_2021\">Source code</a> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/stars/michaelstaib/PublicSpeaking?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=604800\" alt=\"stars\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/last-commit/michaelstaib/PublicSpeaking?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=86400\" alt=\"last commit\">.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-24T14:25:21.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rust-embedded/awesome-embedded-rust","categoryHTML":"<h2>Community</h2><h3>Community Chat Rooms</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://matrix.to/#/#rp-rs:matrix.org\">#rp-rs:matrix.org</a> - For discussion of using Embedded Rust on RP2040 based devices</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-24T14:08:56.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"CodyReichert/awesome-cl","categoryHTML":"<h2>Persistent object databases</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hanshuebner/bknr-datastore\">bknr.datastore</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/hanshuebner/bknr-datastore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">83</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":83,\"repo\":\"hanshuebner/bknr-datastore\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - a CLOS-based lisp-only database in RAM with transaction logging persistence. <a href=\"https:/